:::::'''Garmentmaker:''' Thank you, esteemed guest. And now, I shall begin to unfurl one of the many prophecies.
:::::'''Garmentmaker:''' Let's see... "In the blemish of the night, wherein reach not the dawnlight, the Makrodrakon struck the temple, leaving flames untemperable."
:::::'''Garmentmaker:''' As expected, an obscure scribble of a prophecy that may yet take time to decipher... If you are interested, you might be inclined to interpret it.
:::::'''Garmentmaker:''' Thank you once again for your aid, esteemed guest.
:::;(If {{cx}}{{subst:void|<!--{"$type":"RPG.GameCore.ByCompareItemNum","ItemPair":[{"ItemID":150056,"ItemNum":1}],"Inverse":true}-->}})
